---
title: Garlic and Ginger Beef Noodles with green beans and bell peppers
description: This Asian-inspired garlic and ginger beef noodle dish has several strong flavours at play. Luckily, each one is perfectly balanced creating a taste that's complex and satisfyingly simple all at once.
